flavor_text_entries.gold:
The curved antlers
subtly change the
flow of air to create a strange
space where real­
ity is distorted.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
Those who stare at
its antlers will
gradually lose control of their
senses and be
unable to stand.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
The round balls
found on the
fallen antlers can be ground into a
powder that aids
in sleeping.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
STANTLER’s magnificent antlers were
traded at high prices as works of art.
As a result, this POKéMON was hunted close to extinction by those who were
after the priceless antlers.

flavor_text_entries.legends-arceus:
Its strangely shaped antlers have the power to bewitch those
who see them. Medicine made by grinding up the black orbs
from fallen antlers is an effective treatment for insomnia.
